{
  "stem": "25809.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It wasn't easy, but in those days, there was still a fair amount of food around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was-- when we talk about '43, '44, that was the horror time, when there literally was no food anywhere.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they got by on that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then, my father was talking to the carpenter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he came over and said, well, he said, you know, if there ever is a raid, then-- and they would come into the house-- they just would break the door down-- kick it in.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And maybe you should create a hiding place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he built two new walls in-- in the two connecting rooms, which were connected with sliding doors.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The sliding doors were taken out, and built an extra wall, which was about, oh, about this wide.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'd say about four feet wide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And made the room smaller by exactly the size of a wardrobe, by which you could take the entire inside panel away, and close that panel from the inside in the hiding place.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before we went into hiding, my father had bought a little metal cash box, because he had some shares.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so-- my father was such a klutz, he couldn't even open up a little keyed cash box.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had to show him how to open it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And apparently I was the person that was kind of handy in mechanical things, and he was exactly the opposite.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the cash box were some of his securities, that he had bought and saved over the years, and had got them out of the bank.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know where he kept them, but he kept them first in a hiding place, [INAUDIBLE] in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a cellar there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
